ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectAppointment of the Honorable Steven Garrett MacKinnon and the Honourable Ruby Sahota
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2024-936 of August 8, 2024; and (2) appointing the Honourable STEVEN GARRETT MACKINNON and the Honourable RUBY SAHOTA, members of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, to be members of the Board of Internal Economy of the House of Commons.
